FBIS3-56727 "drsov012_d_94018" FBIS-SOV-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 Regional Affairs Yeltsin Appoints Samara Oblast Representative LD1701105494 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1008 GMT 17 Jan 94 LD1701105494 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow, 17 Jan (ITAR-TASS) -- Yuriy Borodulin has been appointed as the Russian president's representative in Samara Oblast by a decree of Russian President Boris Yeltsin. This was reported by the president's press service.
